  "detailed_description": "Death Road is a solo Top Down Shooter game. Take on the challenge of liberating the earth from a zombies and monsters infestation, using over-the-top weaponry in a world with awesomely stylized graphics. The road journey has never been so much fun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon Category</strong></h2> - Machine Gun, Rockets, Shot-Gun, SMG, Sniper, Fireball, Gatling gun, Ice gun, Bolt gun and Of course Flamethrower.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282620/extras/9701b09490b18c29d8eec3cbc3c414ad.poster.avif?t=1682372405\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282620/extras/9701b09490b18c29d8eec3cbc3c414ad.webm?t=1682372405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282620/extras/9701b09490b18c29d8eec3cbc3c414ad.mp4?t=1682372405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2> - Our world is attacked by Zombies and Monsters. Other soldier troops tried to clean the area but no one survived. A soldier stands to take the responsibility to fight against all zombies and monsters and world hope is relied on him. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282620/extras/231e082ac57f754c45d5dbe94c2aabc7.poster.avif?t=1682372405\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282620/extras/231e082ac57f754c45d5dbe94c2aabc7.webm?t=1682372405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282620/extras/231e082ac57f754c45d5dbe94c2aabc7.mp4?t=1682372405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mission</strong></h2> - One Soldier to Save the World, so Kill one -  Kill All, No Mercy, No Pity, No Regret.",
